msgstr ""
"“Good, Vāseṭṭha. For it is impossible that they should teach the path to "
"that which they neither know nor see."

#. </p><h3>
msgctxt "dn13:20.10"
msgid "2.2. Nisseṇīupamā"
msgstr "2.2. The Simile of the Ladder"

#. </h3><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs21"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc32"></a>
msgctxt "dn13:21.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, vāseṭṭha, puriso cātumahāpathe nisseṇiṃ kareyya pāsādassa "
"ārohaṇāya."
msgstr ""
"Suppose a man was to build a ladder at the crossroads for climbing up to a "
"stilt longhouse."

msgctxt "dn13:21.2"
msgid "Tamenaṃ evaṃ vadeyyuṃ:"
msgstr "They’d say to him:"

#. VAR: yassa tvaṃ → yaṃ tvaṃ (s1-3) | yassa (pts1)
msgctxt "dn13:21.3"
msgid ""
"‘ambho purisa, yassa tvaṃ pāsādassa ārohaṇāya nisseṇiṃ karosi, jānāsi taṃ "
"pāsādaṃ—puratthimāya vā disāya dakkhiṇāya vā disāya pacchimāya vā disāya "
"uttarāya vā disāya ucco vā nīco vā majjhimo vā’ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘Mister, that stilt longhouse that you’re building a ladder for—do you know "
"whether it’s to the north, south, east, or west? Or whether it’s tall or "
"short or medium?’"

msgctxt "dn13:21.4"
msgid "Iti puṭṭho ‘no’ti vadeyya."
msgstr "Asked this, he’d say, ‘No.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs22"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc33"></a>
msgctxt "dn13:22.1"
msgid "Tamenaṃ evaṃ vadeyyuṃ:"
msgstr "They’d say to him:"

msgctxt "dn13:22.2"
msgid ""
"‘ambho purisa, yaṃ tvaṃ na jānāsi, na passasi, tassa tvaṃ pāsādassa "
"ārohaṇāya nisseṇiṃ karosī’ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘Mister, are you building a ladder for a longhouse that you’ve never even "
"known or seen?’"

msgctxt "dn13:22.3"
msgid "Iti puṭṭho ‘āmā’ti vadeyya."
msgstr "Asked this, he’d say, ‘Yes.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc34"></a>
msgctxt "dn13:22.4"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, vāseṭṭha, "
msgstr "What do you think, Vāseṭṭha? "

msgctxt "dn13:22.5"
msgid "nanu evaṃ sante tassa purisassa appāṭihīrakataṃ bhāsitaṃ sampajjatī”ti?"
msgstr ""
