"sampajjatī”ti."
msgstr "“Clearly that’s the case, sir.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.244"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc35"></a>
msgctxt "dn13:22.7"
msgid ""
